headline: Dollar General Is Making a Bold Move by Offering Same-Day Delivery. Why It Could Make or Break the Stock
summary: Dollar General (NYSE: DG) is a business that needs a catalyst to turn things around, desperately.  The large discount retailer is facing many challenges these days.  In December, Dollar General reported its third-quarter results (for the period ending Nov. 1), which were lackluster, yet again.
